Ecological notes : very common in broad-leaved, mixed and carr woodland; heathland and scrub; wetlands including water meadows,
Sphagnum
bog and sedge beds, saltmarsh; unimproved calcareous grassland; old hedges; old sand and gravel workings; gardens; near shore; coastal landslip. iii–x.
